sequenceDiagram
    participant OS as Android OS
    participant Broadcast as SMS Receiver
    participant RegEx as Parsing Engine
    participant Inbox as Pending DB
    participant User as User UI
    participant Ledger as Main DB
    
    OS->>Broadcast: Incoming SMS
    Broadcast->>RegEx: String Payload
    RegEx->>RegEx: Check Bank Filters
    RegEx->>Inbox: Insert Pending Transaction
    Inbox-->>User: Show Badge Notification
    User->>Inbox: Review & Tap Approve
    Inbox->>Ledger: Move to Transactions Table
